OL,3,CNew health standards and labelling
OL,4,Crules to be introduced for baby food
OL,6,FNew government guidelines are being
OL,7,Fintroduced to reduce the amount of
OL,8,Fsugar and salt in baby foods.
OL,10,FManufacturers will be given 18 months
OL,11,Fto implement the new rules for baby
OL,12,Ffoods aimed at children up to 36
OL,13,Fmonths old.
OL,15,FThey will be required to change
OL,16,Frecipes to reduce sugar and salt,
OL,17,Fwithout the use of sweeteners.
