OL,3,CNew health standards and labelling
OL,4,Crules to be introduced for baby food
OL,6,FHigh sugar intake in children's diets
OL,7,Fis a major contributor to rates of
OL,8,Fchildhood obesity in the UK, which is
OL,9,Famong the highest in Western Europe.
OL,11,FObesity currently costs the NHS around
OL,12,F#11.4 billion a year.
OL,14,FThere will also be new rules about
OL,15,Flabelling on baby food to try and
OL,16,Fclamp down on misleading claims about
OL,17,Fingredients.
