OL,3,CNew health standards and labelling
OL,4,Crules to be introduced for baby food
OL,6,FFor example, some products labelled as
OL,7,Fsnacks for babies from seven months
OL,8,Fonwards contradict government
OL,9,Frecommendations that children aged 6-
OL,10,F12 months do not need snacks between
OL,11,Fmeals, only milk.
OL,13,FManufacturers will also be told to
OL,14,Fcease using marketing claims that make
OL,15,Fproducts appear healthier than they
OL,16,Fare - for example, products with
OL,17,Flabels such as "contains no nasties" -
OL,18,Fwhen products may be high in sugar.
